node.text:
First word or emoji that comes to mind? Jupiter... 🤯

Jupiter experiences pretty violent storms and cyclones that reach up to 425mph. That orange spot in the top left is a cyclone known as the Great Red Spot; it’s been spinning for 300 years so far.

image: ©️ NASA JPL
